project:
In the distant western frontier lies a small town called "Wild West Town," once a thriving trade center. However, over time, the town has fallen under the control of a gang of ruthless outlaws who terrorize the residents, plundering and instilling fear in their hearts.

You will take on the role of a solitary gunslinger, driven by a mission of revenge and a belief in justice. By chance, you uncover the outlaws' sinister plot and decide to embark on a journey to cleanse the town. Your goal is to eliminate the enemies lurking in the shadows, liberate the oppressed townsfolk, and restore peace to Wild West Town.

Throughout this challenging adventure, you will face various foes, using your sharpshooting skills and cunning to overcome numerous obstacles, remember to distinguish between evil gangsters and good townspeople, ultimately uncovering the truth hidden in the darkness. Get ready to embrace this quest filled with excitement and glory!
→: Walk  ↑: Jump   E: Shoot   R: Reload
